}}'''The United Kingdom''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the capital, London, along with Aberdeen, Belfast, Birmingham, Blackpool, Brighton, Bristol, Cambridge, Cardiff, Edinburgh, Glasgow, Hull, Ipswich, Leeds, Leicester, Liverpool, Manchester, Milton Keynes, Newcastle, Norwich, Nottingham, Oxford, Sheffield, Southhampton, Staines, Sunderland, Swansea, and Wolverhampton. This adds to a total of 22 English cities, 3 Scottish cities, 2 Welsh cities, and 1 Northern Irish city for a total of 28 cities.
==Information==

In the U.K. it is legal to gamble and to marry as a same-sex couple. Driving age is 17 and graduation age is 18.

On iOS, the United Kingdom provides free healthcare, making characters able to consult doctors and treat [[Diseases|diseases and ailments]] free of charge. However university is not free and characters will still have a tuition fee.

The United Kingdom is one of the few countries that have royalty
